  "title": "Project Manager (M&E Firm - Data Centre Projects) [SAS]",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Oversee the entire project lifecycle from tender to completion.</li>\n  <li>Preferably experienced in leading a team of 10-15 members, including Engineers, Supervisors, Safety Coordinators, Drawing Managers, Drafters, and others.</li>\n  <li>Review and supervise drawing submissions.</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper documentation and approval for materials.</li>\n  <li>Manage subcontractors and ensure effective collaboration.</li>\n  <li>Plan and sequence work to ensure smooth project execution.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with clients, owners, and consultants regarding project requirements and timelines.</li>\n  <li>Address and resolve any issues that arise throughout the project.</li>\n  <li>Ensure the project is completed on time, meets quality standards, and stays within budget.</li>\n  <li>Bring relevant experience to successfully complete the project within time and cost parameters.</li>\n  <li>Control the project budget, manage expenses, and oversee cash flow.<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Electrical Engineering or a related field.</li>\n  <li>5 years of experience as a Project Manager</li>\n  <li>Well versed in testing &amp; commissioning requirements in CX T&amp;C requirements of Data Centres</li>\n  <li>Possess technical, financial, project and contract management knowledge</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
